    "MissionTokens": {
        "Contractor|GroupBountyDescription": [
            "Local law just bounced us a group warrant. They're looking for the capture of several individuals wanted in connection with a major heist, aka\u00a0[Target1],\u00a0[Target2], and\u00a0[Target3].\n\nTake care of the lot in the time allotted, and we're looking a fairly sizable payday.\u00a0\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group",
            "Advocacy have been hunting down a group, but haven't had much luck. Lucky for them, NorthRock is ready to pick up the slack.\n\nWe got a time restricted warrant for:\n- [Target1]\n- [Target2]\n- [Target3]\n\nBe careful when you engage the targets. I don't want any of them slipping the net and costing us credits.\u00a0\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group",
            "I feel like you've proven yourself capable, so I think you should be able to handle this time restricted group warrant. \n\nWe're sending you out to neutralize [Target1], [Target2], and [Target3]. They're most likely not flying together anymore, but at one point they were operating as a pretty cutthroat gang. Racked up quite the hefty felony list before they disbanded.\n\nIt'll be more dangerous trying to capture them all in time, but the payout should be worth it.\n\nFly smart,\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group",
            "Authorities are pretty eager to capture a trio of outlaws in connection with recent crime spree: [Target1], [Target2], and [Target3]. \n\nThey're in the wind at the moment, but I trust that you'll be able to track each and every one of them down.\n\nThe payout for apprehending all three should make up for the extra effort needed to capture them in time.\n\nGood luck,\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group",
            "Northrock got handed a bounty for three criminal associates on the run: [Target1], [Target2], and [Target3]. \n\nIf they're smart, chances are they split up, so be ready to hunt them down individually.\n\nGood news is that the pay should make dealing with tight time restriction and extra travel worth it.\n\nFly safe,\n\nBraden Corchado\nLogistics Officer - Stanton Branch\nNorthrock Service Group"
        ],
        "Contractor": [
            "Northrock Service Group"
        ]
    },
